│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ *   **Source Code Location:** The crash is at `llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp:13364`, which corresponds to the line `TerminatorInst *TI = BB->getTerminator();`. This   │
│ confirms that `BB` is the problematic variable.                                                                                                                                          │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
