│ In the provided IR, the vectorizer might try to vectorize a group of PHI nodes in `bb12`, including `%phi17`. One of the operands of `%phi17` is `%srem`, which is an instruction in     │
│ `bb5`. If the vectorizer analyzes the operands of these PHIs, it will encounter `%srem`.                                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
